{"tid":475225,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何志平涉賄賂非洲官員　罪成可囚20年","createTime":"2017-11-21T02:32:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T02:43:41.000Z","uid":20933,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ad84d82ed5a12859bc08915e7ee153e405674903","tid":475225,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T02:32:24.000Z","msg":"香港前民政事務局局長何志平與塞內加爾前外長，涉嫌代表一間中國能源公司賄賂非洲官員，金額數以百萬美元計，部份交易在聯合國門廳內進行。二人周末在紐約被捕。<br />\n<br />\n何志平與加迪奧（Cheikh Gadio）被指為一間中國能源公司向乍得和烏干達公司行賄，以獲取石油生意。二人涉嫌以200萬美元（約1,560萬港元）賄賂乍得總統「取得寶貴的石油開採權」；又將50萬美元（約390萬港元）款項存入烏干達外長庫泰薩（Sam Kutesa）的戶口。賄款之中約100萬美元（約780萬港元）是以捐款為名，經紐約銀行系統匯款。<br />\n<br />\n何志平又向烏干達外長和總統送禮並承諾將來提供利益，包括分享一間合營公司利潤。<br />\n<br />\n紐約曼哈頓署理聯邦檢察官金賢俊（Joon H. Kim）發表聲明，指「在一宗跨越全球的國際貪污案中，何志平與加迪奧涉嫌以一間中國能源企業的名義，串謀賄賂非洲政府官員」。美國署助理司法部長勃朗哥（Kenneth A. Blanco）表示，二人的貪污行為損害經濟，破壞公眾對自由市場的信心。"},{"pid":"283b467b406095065af8b48189a15f874681b625","tid":475225,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T02:34:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171121/large/1511217028_e75b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171121%2Flarge%2F1511217028_e75b.jpg&h=429b75a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n68歲的何志平和61歲的加迪奧，各被控以違反海外貪污行為法及洗錢罪，一旦罪成最高可被判20年。何志平2002年任民政事務局局長，2007年卸任後主力從事國民外交工作，擔任「中華能源基金會」常務副主席兼秘書長。"},{"pid":"abc0b3e252b5b916c32ef71f356f304a4f097f77","tid":475225,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T02:37:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171121/57484014\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171121%2F57484014&d=YHB6s8ga2I4eb32L6MIQwDANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=abfe6aa2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171121%2F57484014&h=d01c8453\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171121/57484014</a>"},{"pid":"17c342b950f6e8ebcc69c605d91cd2490c9b40bd","tid":475225,"uid":19557,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T02:39:02.000Z","msg":"好波 一帶一賂"},{"pid":"a7289bbdc78aebeed1fe2bdfa5603cfce6c4914a","tid":475225,"uid":45613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T02:40:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d87ef1140f404037bd4a0c92ab0f3cf567d2a78","tid":475225,"uid":31269,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T02:41:41.000Z","msg":"你使橫手搞鐵路，美國佬未必會做你，你搞石油佢仲唔立即同你開拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6486af8a7540764cae80744d8026f3844085b7ad","tid":475225,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T02:43:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6Tp6DLV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F6Tp6DLV.gif&h=b1d99106&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}